# Title: Disable of ETW Trace - Powershell
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-06-28
# Level: high
# Description: Detects usage of powershell cmdlets to disable or remove ETW trace sessions
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1070, attack.t1685, car.2016-04-002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_etw_trace_evasion.yml

ScriptBlockText="*Remove-EtwTraceProvider *" OR (ScriptBlockText="*Set-EtwTraceProvider *" ScriptBlockText="*0x11*")